        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer673498871" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11741909981693475536">Absolutely wonderful book. This is a collection of stores that will have you crying, checking for monsters under the bed, and wondering how the hell Joe Hill came up with that.<br/><br/>Comparisons to Joe&apos;s dad will be unavoidable, especially from those of us who read Night Shift and Skeleton Crew at a certain age ... and though I believe Joe has more than earned the right to be far, far out of his father&apos;s shadow, I say with love that the comparisons are well-deserved. This is a sensational collection, a</span>
  <span id="freeText11741909981693475536" style="display:none">Absolutely wonderful book. This is a collection of stores that will have you crying, checking for monsters under the bed, and wondering how the hell Joe Hill came up with that.<br /><br />Comparisons to Joe's dad will be unavoidable, especially from those of us who read Night Shift and Skeleton Crew at a certain age ... and though I believe Joe has more than earned the right to be far, far out of his father's shadow, I say with love that the comparisons are well-deserved. This is a sensational collection, and very much worth your time.</span>
